/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The vantage point is high, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, flanked by towering buildings on one side and verdant trees on the other. The buildings, predominantly white and gray, rise high into the sky, their windows reflecting the sunlight. The trees, on the other hand, are a mix of green and brown, their leaves rustling in the breeze. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with fluffy white clouds. The sun shines brightly, casting long shadows and bathing the scene in a warm glow.
